Version 0

Description
    A MVP backend, website and PWA

Abilities 
    
    1. Create a graph and add node characteristics
    2. Store the graph and node characteristics in a file that can be loaded later
    3. Find a path from home node to destination node
    4. Display the shortest path to the user
   


Version 1

Description
    Tending towards a viable mobile web app

Abilities 

    1. QR code generation upon node creation
    2. QR code read
    3. Auto update home node on reading the current QR codej
        a. Find the path to destination again
        b. Return the shortest path
